her defaults.custom exists', confirming that the bug was originally an incorrect placement inside the nested conditional.\n\n3. Test file (apps/dashboard/pkg/migration/schemaversion/v38_test.go): The test case at line 443 -- 'table with missing defaults.custom but overrides with custom.displayMode' -- explicitly exercises this failure path. It provides table panels where defaults has no custom key but overrides contain custom.displayMode entries, and expects those overrides to be correctly migrated to custom.cellOptions."
